text: Ærest on linleage middewearde & on hean leage westewearde & an gabuldene eastewearde.
Þanne on stapolas & an beonnan þorn.
Ðonne an tuddeles þorn & an hroces wylle.
Þonne on wulf beorh & an tuddan ham westeweardne.
Þanne on brading leage westeweardne & on fearn lege westewearde.
Þonne an lawern wylle & an pegdes setl eastewerd.
Ærest on hroces wylle, þanne up on þæne weg oþ grenan hlinc.
Þanon on þa hegeræwe on humbor ford.
Þanon on eabbincg wylle þanne on risc broc .
Þanon on þa westran fearn leage.
Þanne on þæt land þe æþelswyþ cwen & Aþelbold ealdorman him geþingedon æt Aþulfe cynge.
